Start a local HTTP/WebSocket bridge over daemon IPC

Usage: mxr web [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --host <HOST>  [default: 127.0.0.1]
      --port <PORT>  [default: 0]
      --print-url    
  -h, --help         Print help
